      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not just a setback though. it's debt. massive, life-ruining debt. every time I close my eyes I see the numbers and the shame. i feel like if i just showed up at my door, they'd see me for what i actually am: a failure. it feels like the only way to actually stop the feeling is to just stop everything. is there even any point in trying to recover when the damage is this permanent?",
