      "content": "but that’s just easy for someone to say. \"it's worth exploring\"... but i've already explored it. there's no counselor or advisor that can undo ten years of lives being ruined by my mistakes. the shame is so heavy I literally can't breathe. it feels like the only way to truly be honest with my family, and the only way to actually find any peace from this, is to just not be here anymore. it feels like the only logical way to end the embarrassment and the debt for everyone.",
